description: The Feeding Frenzy food truck is serving up the FUN with the most delicious gourmet funnel cakes, "carnival" food and mouth-watering lemonade you'll ever taste."Worlds Best Tasting Carnival Food, Funnel Cakes, Desserts & More"!We hope you have fun browsing our website to see all of the delicious foods and desserts we can serve up, from hand dipped corn dogs, chili cheese dogs, nachos, funnel cakes, amazing fried desserts and don't forget our homemade mouth watering regular and strawberry lemonade. For carnivals, fairs, special events and more. We're sure you'll enjoy.  You'll only find the best at the Feeding Frenzy Truck
name: The Feeding Frenzy
